        <updateDate>2012-08-14T16:06:51Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Validating Entitlement Recipients through Indicated Federal Immigration Status Act of 2012 or the VERIFI Act of 2012 - Prohibits a person from receiving a federal public benefit unless such person is in &quot;satisfactory immigration status&quot; in accordance with the Systematic Alien Verification for Entitlements (SAVE) program.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
